      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the<strong> pepper strips</strong> and <strong>torn mushrooms</strong> with a splash of <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until everything has softened</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
