    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong>, <strong>drained</strong> <strong>butter beans</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar </strong>to the pan with the vegetables</p><p>Stir in the<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> and 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[380ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 12-15 min further or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>veggie goulash</strong></p>",
